name: The Angel on Skypark and Crenshaw
description:
I pass by here now and then and often wonder if they made it.

Skypark and Crenshaw is a busy 4x6-lane intersection in Los Angeles County. You can see the mark from a distance here:
https://www.google.com/maps/@33.8014783,-118.3283898,3a,15y,135.16h,82t/data=!3m6!1e1!3m4!1sm9YQw7ivc6DyF47KN2mT9A!2e0!7i16384!8i8192

"You've arrived at your destination."
